column1: We just happened upon this restaurant... so lucky they had a table available. It was our favorite dining experience in Prague. Very fresh ingredients well-prep...
A little old-fashioned in my opinion, but a safe bet for a good dining experience. View of the Charles Bridge and Castle really nice.
This was the best restaurant we experienced in Budapest, we thought better than even Caviar & Bull. Excellent food, in particular the starters -- the foie gras...
The food was very good. We had the larger menu plus caviar service, and didn't think it was too much food (although we didn't have lunch knowing we'd be dining ...
